<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَلَا يَمْنَعُ وُجُوبَهَا دَيْنٌ؛ إِلَّا مَعَ طَلَبٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَتَجِبُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> عَلَى كُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> إِذَا كَانَتْ فَاضِلَةً عَنِ:<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- نَفَقَةٍ وَاجِبَةٍ يَوْمَ العِيدِ وَلَيْلَتَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَمَا يَحْتَاجُهُ مِنْ مَسْكَنٍ، وَخَادِمٍ، وَدَابَّةٍ، وَكُتُبِ عِلْمٍ يَحْتَاجُهَا لِنَظَرٍ وَحِفْظٍ، وَثِيَابِ بِذْلَةٍ وَنَحْوِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> فَيُخْرِجُ عَنْ:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> نَفْسِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَعَنْ كُلِّ مُسْلِمٍ يَمُونُه.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- فَإِنْ لَمْ يَجِدْ لِجَمِيعِهِمْ؛<span style="color:#006d98"> بَدَأَ:</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> بِنَفْسِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> فَزَوْجَتِهِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> فَرَقِيقِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>